    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>Frost-skinned corpses bound by barrow-magic, their hollow eyes glowing faint green. Draugr thralls are the most numerous of the undead, raised in droves from Svellheim's cairns to serve as shock troops. They move with jerking, mechanical gaits — unfeeling, unthinking, and utterly relentless. Their frozen grasp can slow even the hardiest warrior.</p>",
